OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FChance of a
OL,6,Ffew showers across Orkney this
OL,7,Fevening, otheriwse it will be dry.
OL,8,FThis will leave the Isles mostly dry
OL,9,Fwith clear spells through the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTuesday:FThe day will stay dry with
OL,12,Fsunny spells, the best of these over
OL,13,FOrkney. A moderate southeast wind.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,16,Fband of rain will push north through
OL,17,FWednesday with scattered showers
OL,18,Ffollowing during Thursday. These
OL,19,Fshowers clear Thursday night to leave
OL,20,FFriday dry but cloudy.
